* The quality of most diphthongs ({{IPA|/uɪ, ei, øy, ɛɪ, œʏ, əʊ, ɞʊ/}}) is close to the canonical values of the IPA symbols used to transcribe them.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=241}}
* The starting points of {{IPA|/aɪ, aʊ/}} are near-open central {{IPAblink|ɐ}}. The ending points are {{IPAblink|ɪ}} and {{IPAblink|ʊ}}, close to the canonical values of the IPA symbols used to transcribe them.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=241}}
* The starting points of the centering diphthongs {{IPA|/iə, eə, ɛə/}} are close to the canonical values of the IPA symbols used to transcribe them ({{IPA|[{{IPA link|i}}, {{IPA link|e}}, {{IPA link|ɛ}}]}}), whereas their ending points are not fully central but centralized front; {{IPAblink|e|ë}} in the case of {{IPA|/iə/}}, {{IPAblink|e̞|ë̞}} in the case of {{IPA|/eə, ɛə/}}.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=241}}

===Prosody===
Stress location is largely the same as in Belgian Standard Dutch. In loanwords from French, the original word-final stress is often preserved, as in {{IPA|[kəˈdaʊ]}} 'cadeau'.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=242}}

===Sample===
The sample text is a reading of the first sentence of [[The North Wind and the Sun]]. The orthographic version is written in Standard Dutch.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|pp=239, 245}}

====Phonetic transcription====
{{IPA|[də ˈnœrdərβ̞ɪnt ʔɛn də zɔn ˈʔadən ən dɪsˈkøːsə ˈɛvə də vɾoːx {{!}} β̞i van ən tβ̞iː də ˈstɛɾəkstə β̞as {{!}} tʏn dʏɪ ʒyst ˈɛmant v̥œrˈbɛːkɔm bə nən ˈdɪkə ˈβ̞aɾəmə ja̰s a̰ːn]}}{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=245}}

====Orthographic version====
De noordenwind en de zon hadden een discussie over de vraag wie van hun tweeën de sterkste was, toen er juist iemand voorbij kwam met een dikke, warme jas aan.{{sfnp|Peters|2010|p=245}}

